main event: A witness in Jonesboro, Arkansas reported an unidentified observation in 1965.
interesting points: The object was seen at night around 6 PM.
The object appeared to be round and blurry, and the witness could not make out any details.
The object moved quickly and was not stationary.
The letter indicates that the information provided was not sufficient for evaluation.
The letter is a response from Project Blue Book, the official U.S. Air Force investigation of UFOs.
